creator: SignOnSite
descriptionHtml:
SignOnSite is an app that matches workers in the construction industry with nearby construction companies running and managing construction sites.
The SignOnSite app revolutionises worksite safety by allowing you to SignOn from anywhere on site - directly from your smartphone. By creating an account with SignOnSite you can:
- check in to any companies sites using the system (without visiting the site office to sign the paper register)
- access daily briefings and toolbox talk information posted by the builder for the site
- share your account details via a digital site-specific induction form, including the sharing of your credentials and their status
- get evacuation notification alerts if an emergency or drill occurs on the site
descriptionShort: SignOnSite allows you to SignOn as soon as you arrive to site.

The SignOnSite app revolutionises worksite safety by allowing you to SignOn from anywhere on site - directly from your smartphone. By creating an account with SignOnSite you can:
- check in to any companies sites using the system (without visiting the site office to sign the paper register)
- access daily briefings and toolbox talk information posted by the builder for the site
- share your account details via a digital site-specific induction form, including the sharing of your credentials and their status
- get evacuation notification alerts if an emergency or drill occurs on the site
descriptionShort: SignOnSite allows you to SignOn as soon as you arrive to site.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fixed an issue where site docs tab would show blank screen when the network call was still trying to get the data.

Fixed an issue where Pixel and some other devices cannot take photos with the camera in the induction form.

descriptionHtml:
SignOnSite is an app that matches workers in the construction industry with nearby construction companies running and managing construction sites.
The SignOnSite app revolutionises worksite safety by allowing you to SignOn from anywhere on site - directly from your smartphone. By creating an account with SignOnSite you can:
- check in to any companies sites using the system (without visiting the site office to sign the paper register)
- access daily briefings and toolbox talk information posted by the builder for the site
- share your account details via a digital site-specific induction form, including the sharing of your credentials and their status
- get evacuation notification alerts if an emergency or drill occurs on the site
